“Alexander, come back to sleep…” 

I just need to write something down — like a full draft, three footnotes, and a title... 🫣

Join the Legal & Legislative Department under FEU Psychology Society – where your midnight thoughts become tomorrow’s policy! 💭☝️

If you’re young, scrappy, and obsessed with legal docs and proofreading contracts, then don’t throw away your shot – apply to L&L and be in the room where it happens! 🌟

I just need to write something down — like a full draft, three footnotes, and a title... 🫣

Join the Legal & Legislative Department under FEU Psychology Society – where your midnight thoughts become tomorrow’s policy! 💭☝️

If you’re young, scrappy, and obsessed with legal docs and proofreading contracts, then don’t throw away your shot – apply to L&L and be in the room where it happens! 🌟

𝐁𝐞 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐒𝐌𝐈𝐋𝐄, 𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐬! 🎭

Do you want to be part of the smile that never fades, the voices that welcome, and the leaders that empower? If yes, then the 𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐒𝐭𝐮𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐂𝐨𝐮𝐧𝐜𝐢𝐥 is your place!🩷

Just like how behind every mask lies a story—within the offices of the ITHM Student Council lies your unwritten journey, waiting to cultivate your leadership potential!✨

𝐓𝐨𝐠𝐞𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫, 𝐥𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐜𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐭𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐟𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐚𝐥 𝐨𝐟 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐂𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐮𝐧𝐢𝐭𝐲.🎊

🔗 Join here: https://forms.cloud.microsoft/r/BVPMhCkmqF

message.text:
𝐁𝐞 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐒𝐌𝐈𝐋𝐄, 𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐬! 🎭

Do you want to be part of the smile that never fades, the voices that welcome, and the leaders that empower? If yes, then the 𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐒𝐭𝐮𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐂𝐨𝐮𝐧𝐜𝐢𝐥 is your place!🩷

Just like how behind every mask lies a story—within the offices of the ITHM Student Council lies your unwritten journey, waiting to cultivate your leadership potential!✨

𝐓𝐨𝐠𝐞𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫, 𝐥𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐜𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐭𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐟𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐚𝐥 𝐨𝐟 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐂𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐮𝐧𝐢𝐭𝐲.🎊

Join with a smile!—Because here in ITHM Student Council, 𝐁𝐢𝐝𝐚 𝐚𝐧𝐠 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞, at 𝐁𝐢𝐝𝐚  𝐤𝐚!

🔗 Join here: https://forms.cloud.microsoft/r/BVPMhCkmqF

Pubmat by: Maia De Jesus, Alexi Margarette Montecastro
Caption by: Antonette Zaballero
 
#BidaSmileSaITHM
#TamHunt2025
#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil
